{"tid":395500,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Teen Wolf Season6","createTime":"2017-09-10T23:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T15:54:19.000Z","uid":60500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0b7b291883a26affc05208dc05cab5dcd5431f7c","tid":395500,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:46:49.000Z","msg":"呢套咁正既野竟然冇人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後一季啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca27cba8c1e8b9ebefec061916334433ef93d50","tid":395500,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/41pcnexw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F41pcnexw&h=f9592d99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d631de270c6cef1a04d005dbf8dfe137593d0b32","tid":395500,"uid":126247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:32:06.000Z","msg":"不如你介紹下,講下有咩好睇"},{"pid":"1095057559162ee6acd009124f20236d682a7fc4","tid":395500,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:08:03.000Z","msg":"維基簡介：<br />\n<br />\n該劇圍繞著Scott McCall（泰勒&middot;珀西飾）在Beacon山高中的生活。一天晚上他和他的好朋友 Stiles (綽號，劇組未透漏全名，只說過很難唸，Genim為其中一集中紙上出現的，但真實性不可知) Stilinski（狄倫&middot;歐布萊恩飾）拉他去找屍體壯膽時他被狼人咬傷，從此他的生活急劇變化。Stiles發現後幫助他克服。<br />\n<br />\nScott數日回到當晚被咬的地方尋找自己丟失的助吸器時碰到了Derek Hale（泰勒&middot;霍奇林飾），獲得狼人力量的Scott也進入曲棍球隊並和新來的轉學生Allison Argent（克莉絲朵&middot;里德飾）展開戀情。在和Allison的首次約會正好是滿月，控制不住自己的Scott找藉口離開並發現在屋檐上的Derek也是狼人。Derek知道後威脅Scott退出曲棍球隊並和Allison分手。<br />\n<br />\n曲棍球隊隊長Jackson Whittemore（Colton Haynes飾）懷疑Scott使用了違禁藥品，於是威脅Scott發現真相後要告訴Allison，Scott在隊伍中的表現也讓Jackson的女友Lydia Martin（Holland Roden飾）對Scott產生好感。而就在某天晚上Scott和Derek在森林中被獵人攻擊，而這個獵人竟然是Allison的父親，更讓Scott想不到的是Argent家族是一個獵人家族。"},{"pid":"2751993758070b7694f34b71fa2fd55802c56937","tid":395500,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"呢套劇除左Teenage Drama之外既重點就係超自然生物<br />\n頭一兩季會聚焦係狼人身上，後來引入埋女妖、狐妖、奇美拉等等既種族<br />\n基本上8成角色都係超自然生物<br />\n而另外一樣吸引到我繼續睇既野係佢既動作場面拍得好好 唔似Arrow season3&amp;4咁垃圾，係真係令觀眾睇到好肉緊<br />\n有啲鏡頭真實得有啲嘔心，今季有一幕一堆死老鼠嚇親我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dac6764769f09ae41f5a688aa9d726969e9764e","tid":395500,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:15:39.000Z","msg":"Youtube搵到啲fight scenes<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GUvDzqcCSrI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGUvDzqcCSrI&d=5ay%2F%2FW2H93mD75sgs%2Fvw00kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=96ef310d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GUvDzqcCSrI</a>"},{"pid":"9488bf443d120ec5396326b2f7f8f9fc49a8da16","tid":395500,"uid":144166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"巴打識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc46cbe129d72866357d4e64d497692b0d48084e","tid":395500,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:12:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後4集啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c06cec61997d42f5f8f96ce13f6f11230f40e7","tid":395500,"uid":230271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:54:19.000Z","msg":"識貨！"}]}